Element fired two more missiles at the back of Abominus's head, and then 
Mantle remembered something that he had picked up from Prowls mind when they 
had a short time to talk. He gave the order to seperate and Element split 
into the five seperate bots.

"Ok, guys," Mantle said, "Focus shots on the gestalts. I have to talk to 
Prowl." With that he hovered off and over to Prowl.

"Hello, Prowl," he said as he approached, "we were talking about a city 
before the battle started, but we never got to finish that."
